commitResults.messageTitle: Level 1: Added the Greet, Echo and Exit features
Level 2: Added Add and List features
Removed trailing and leading whitespaces entered by user
Level 3: Mark task as completed and uncompleted
Level 4: Added ToDo, Event, Deadline tasks
Level 8: Add Date and time feature
commitResults.messageBody:
Changed Deadline and Event tasks dates to LocalDate and handled case
where date passed in is invalid.

Added Ui, Storage, Parser and various Command classes. Changed
unmark error message which had a typo.

commitResults.messageTitle: Organise the classes into the various packages
commitResults.messageBody:
Added 3 packages, namely duke, duke.task and duke.command. The
classes were split into one of the 3 packages.

commitResults.messageTitle: Change class name in Gradle File
commitResults.messageBody: Modified the main class name under application in Build.Gradle
Added ParserTest which tests the Parser class.
Added EventTest and DeadlineTest classes.
Changed WrongCommand message.

Added FindCommand class to handle find command. Edited Parser class
to handle the FindCommand case. Edited Task class to check if the
task contains the keyword.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add JavaDoc to all of the classes and public methods
commitResults.messageBody: Added JavaDocs for all of the classes and to the public methods.

commitResults.messageTitle: Refactored code to meet coding standard
commitResults.messageBody: Changed from Integer class to int for position in deleteCommand.

Added MainWindow, Main and DialogBox classes and their respective
FXML files. Added some padding to the label and resolved issue
where screen would shift slightly to the right.

commitResults.messageTitle: Fix some bugs in coding quality
commitResults.messageBody:
Changed the import statment for Parser from duke.command.* to the various
duke.command classes. Renamed some variables and reduced code
duplication.
Added assert statements into Parser class.
Removed redundant uses of this in code. Changed some variable names.
Introduced Undo Feature and Added CommandHistory class.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add switch statments and abstract out code
commitResults.messageBody:
Added switch statments and abstracted out some lines of code to
improve code quality.
Updated the markdown for the user guide.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add bye command to user guide
commitResults.messageBody: Added description and explanation of bye command in user guide.

commitResults.messageTitle: Improve code quality and update aesthetics of GUI
commitResults.messageBody:
Improved code quality for all classes and changed the
colour of dialog boxes. Ui.png was also updated.

Updated the formatting for message printed by
list command.

Updated user guide by inserting horizontal lines
after each feature.
Added Acknowledgements for images used.
